               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18080601-104-cd610" type="crimeDate">17th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080601-104-off609 t18080601-104-cd610"></join>, a saw, value 4 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18080601-104-victim858" type="victimName">
                     Robert 
                     Roberts
                  <interp inst="t18080601-104-victim858" type="surname" value="Roberts"></interp>
